## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="2b23b-102"><xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.RowContextMenuStripNeeded>只發生事件時<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView>控制項<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.DataSource%2A>屬性設定或其<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.VirtualMode%2A>屬性是`true`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2b23b-102">The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.RowContextMenuStripNeeded> event occurs only when the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView> control <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.DataSource%2A> property is set or its <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.VirtualMode%2A> property is `true`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2b23b-103">處理<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.RowContextMenuStripNeeded>事件很實用，當您想要顯示的捷徑功能表，取決於資料列的目前狀態或包含的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2b23b-103">Handling the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.RowContextMenuStripNeeded> event is useful when you want to display a shortcut menu determined by a row's current state or the values it contains.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="2b23b-104">當您處理<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.RowContextMenuStripNeeded>您指定的處理常式中的捷徑功能表會顯示事件，每當使用者以滑鼠右鍵按一下資料列除非<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.CellContextMenuStripNeeded>事件覆寫已按下的特定資料格的捷徑功能表。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2b23b-104">When you handle the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.RowContextMenuStripNeeded> event, the shortcut menu that you specify in the handler is shown whenever the user right-clicks a row unless the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.CellContextMenuStripNeeded> event overrides the shortcut menu for the specific cell that was clicked.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="2b23b-105"><xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.RowContextMenuStripNeeded>事件也會發生值<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewRow.ContextMenuStrip%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>擷取屬性，或是以程式設計的方式，或當使用者按一下滑鼠右鍵資料列。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2b23b-105">The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.RowContextMenuStripNeeded> event also occurs whenever the value of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewRow.ContextMenuStrip%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property is retrieved, either programmatically or when the user right-clicks a row.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="2b23b-106">您可以使用<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewRowContextMenuStripNeededEventArgs.RowIndex%2A>屬性來判斷的值或資料列的狀態變更或修改使用這項資訊<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewRowContextMenuStripNeededEventArgs.ContextMenuStrip%2A>屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2b23b-106">You can use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewRowContextMenuStripNeededEventArgs.RowIndex%2A> property to determine the state of a row or the values it contains, and use this information to change or modify the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewRowContextMenuStripNeededEventArgs.ContextMenuStrip%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2b23b-107">這個屬性會使用資料列的值初始化<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewRow.ContextMenuStrip%2A>事件值會覆寫的屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2b23b-107">This property is initialized with the value of the row <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewRow.ContextMenuStrip%2A> property, which the event value overrides.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="2b23b-108">處理<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.RowContextMenuStripNeeded>事件時使用大量的資料，以避免效能的負面影響的資料列設定<xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewRow.ContextMenuStrip%2A>多個資料列的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2b23b-108">Handle the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.RowContextMenuStripNeeded> event when working with large amounts of data to avoid the performance penalties of setting the row <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewRow.ContextMenuStrip%2A> value for multiple rows.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2b23b-109">如需詳細資訊，請參閱[縮放 Windows Form DataGridView 控制項的最佳作法](~/docs/framework/winforms/controls/best-practices-for-scaling-the-windows-forms-datagridview-control.md)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2b23b-109">For more information, see [Best Practices for Scaling the Windows Forms DataGridView Control](~/docs/framework/winforms/controls/best-practices-for-scaling-the-windows-forms-datagridview-control.md).</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="2b23b-110">如需處理事件的詳細資訊，請參閱[NIB： 使用事件](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/01e4f1bc-e55e-413f-98c7-6588493e5f67)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2b23b-110">For more information about handling events, see [NIB: Consuming Events](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/01e4f1bc-e55e-413f-98c7-6588493e5f67).</span></span>  
  
   
  
